# Edge Function Boundaries

- Keep service role keys and third-party secrets out of frontend files.
- Preserve function contracts unless a change is explicit and coordinated.
- If a function needs new env vars, document them in `.env.example` and deployment notes.
- If a function needs schema changes, add a migration in `supabase/migrations/`.
- Prefer production-safe defaults and minimal PII in logs.
